name: Mens Diverged Tribe Tee
description:
Our newest tee, the Diverged Tribal tee!  Featuring a bony tribal indian skull, eyes beading with the Aberrant logos.  This tee represents that through life until death, you see the Aberrant way no matter how old.  Diverge From Normal, and be yourself!

Printed on Next Level Apparel, one of the softest on the market!
90% cotton/10% poly
4.3-oz. 
32-singles cotton for extreme softness

SUPPLY IS LIMITED, AFTER PURCHASE YOU WILL RECEIVE AN EMAIL TO INFORM YOU OF STOCK AVAILABILITY!
